# GitNexus is the primary navigation tool

This repo is indexed by GitNexus as **__GITNEXUS_REPO__**. Check live stats: `READ gitnexus://repo/__GITNEXUS_REPO__/context`. Use graph tools BEFORE Grep / Glob / Read / SemanticSearch for **all code reasoning** (not only the first lookup).

## Mandatory workflow chain

Run tools in this order â€” do not skip steps:

```
1. READ gitnexus://repo/__GITNEXUS_REPO__/context     â†’ staleness check (always first)
2. gitnexus_query({query, task_context, goal})         â†’ orient by concept / execution flow
3. gitnexus_context({name}) or context({uid})          â†’ deep dive on one symbol
4. gitnexus_cypher({query, params})                      â†’ structural precision (READ schema first)
5. gitnexus_impact({target, direction: "upstream"})    â†’ BEFORE editing any symbol
6. gitnexus_detect_changes({scope})                    â†’ BEFORE committing / PR review
```

> **Cursor agents:** stale index â†’ `npm run gitnexus:agent-refresh` autonomously. Humans/CI: `npm run gitnexus:refresh`.

