## Index freshness (graph + embeddings)

- After meaningful code changes: `npm run gitnexus:refresh` (includes `--embeddings`)
- Pre-commit hook runs incremental refresh when hooks installed (`npm run hooks:install`)
- **Missing embeddings** (`stats.embeddings === 0` with symbols indexed) = stale â€” `agent-refresh` rebuilds vectors
- Embeddings preserved on incremental refresh; `--drop-embeddings` only when rebuilding vectors intentionally
- If MCP says stale after refresh, restart Cursor to reload the MCP server

## MCP unreachable â€” warn immediately

If GitNexus MCP fails, tell the user: _"GitNexus MCP is unreachable â€” impact/detect_changes/graph queries unavailable. Falling back to Grep/Read without structural safety checks."_ Do NOT silently fall back. Confirm backend health with `npm run gitnexus:doctor` (probes the GitNexus CLI + registry).

