## Workspace contract (non-negotiable)

- `impact` BEFORE editing any function / class / method â€” report blast radius
- `detect_changes` BEFORE committing
- Warn on HIGH / CRITICAL risk before proceeding
- NEVER find-and-replace renames â€” use `rename`

